    <briefdescription>
<para>DNS Service Discovery. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>This API enables services to be advertised via DNS. To advertise a service, system or application code should use <ref refid="group__dns__sd_1ga96abc525d755c138304f07cdd2d9e1c2" kindref="member">DNS_SD_REGISTER_TCP_SERVICE</ref> or <ref refid="group__dns__sd_1gaf8abe0968552213d46b49be16c1f21d6" kindref="member">DNS_SD_REGISTER_UDP_SERVICE</ref>.</para>
<para><simplesect kind="see"><para><ulink url="https://tools.ietf.org/html/rfc6763">RFC 6763</ulink></para>
